      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.hxVH1ncHE1mijpY0]{Chronomancy Anchor}</p>\n<p>Once per day, you can cast any spell you know that has a casting time of a standard action or less as a full action instead. After you successfully cast this spell, you can cast a second spell without taking an action (though it still uses a spell slot). The second spell must have a casting time of a standard action or less and be of a level no greater than the level of the first spell you cast minus 2. If you cast the second spell, you lose your standard action on your next turn.</p>"
